2003-03-11 18:00  parshin

	* efltk/db/Fl_Database.h, efltk/db/Fl_ODBC_Database.h,
	efltk/db/Fl_Query.h, src/core/Fl_Util.cpp, src/db/Fl_Database.cpp,
